# MCP Template Development Guide

## Project Overview
This is an MCP (Model Context Protocol) server template with TypeScript, providing dual transport support (stdio/HTTP), comprehensive testing, and production-ready patterns.

## Key Files to Customize

### üîß Essential Customization Points
- **[package.json](mdc:package.json)** - Update `name`, `description`, and `author` fields
- **[src/index.ts](mdc:src/index.ts)** - Replace example tools with your custom tools (lines 43-95 contain the tool definitions)
- **[LICENSE](mdc:LICENSE)** - Update copyright holder name
- **[.env.example](mdc:.env.example)** - Add your required environment variables

